reviews.text: Came for dinner and drinks. 1-1 beer offer before 9 pm. But strictly can only be taken by same person! Also can't have visitors come take a seat and share with you without ordering their own, even though there are plenty of seats around..
Decent, no-frills bar with outdoor seating, fairly low prices, quick service and a loud crowd. Can be a great time depending on your preferences, but what you see is what you get.

Friendly staff and good food, although the staff won't let you sit by the tables closer to the street on the patio as they keep them empty to attract pedestrian. Was disapointed to have to sit at the back crammed between three crowed tables while the was 3 beautiful street side tables available.
Good place to cheer up with friends . Can enjoy happy hour up to 9 PM

Good value about 45 hkd per pint during happy hour
Double price after 9pm
